<h2>RTSA Suite PRO Capabilities</h2>

<ul>
<li><strong>Display modes:</strong> Live trace, waterfall, persistence, density, wrapped spectrum.</li>
<li><strong>Modulation:</strong> CW, sweep, noise, pulse, FSK, BPSK, ASK, QPSK, QPSK-C, 16-QAM through 4096-QAM, OFDM, raster image, echo/reflection.</li>
<li><strong>Direction finding:</strong> Real-time 3D bearing with elevation, cross-bearings, mobile truck support, GPS position solving, 3D map view.</li>
<li><strong>Recording:</strong> 24/7 I/Q streaming up to 245 MHz, SigMF format, replay-as-live.</li>
<li><strong>Triggers:</strong> Frequency mask, level, pulse, external, software-defined.</li>
<li><strong>Visual programming:</strong> Block-based pipeline editor with custom Python and C++ blocks.</li>
<li><strong>Data export:</strong> SigMF, KML, KMZ, GeoJSON, NMEA, CSV, MQTT, REST API.</li>
</ul>

