<h1 id="appG">Appendix G: Education Pathways</h1>

<h2>Universities with Strong RF / Microwave Programs</h2>

<h3>United States</h3>
<p>MIT (Lincoln Lab affiliation), Stanford (BWRC ties), UC Berkeley (BWRC), Georgia Tech (GTRI), University of Michigan (Radlab), University of Texas Austin (WNCG), Virginia Tech (Wireless@VT), USC, Carnegie Mellon.</p>

<h3>Europe</h3>
<p>ETH Zurich (IIS), TU Munich (Hochfrequenztechnik), KTH Stockholm (Wireless@KTH), Imperial College London, TU Delft, Aalborg University.</p>

