<h2>Closing Note</h2>

<p>These appendices are designed to be referenced repeatedly. The glossary lookup, math formulas, product comparisons, quick-reference tables, quiz keys, education pathways, employer lists, standards summaries, and tool ecosystem entries all reduce friction in daily work. A book that lives on the bench earns its keep through these reference sections more than through any single read of the main chapters.</p>


